
bin2xtc_aa.c
 convert plain binary format to xtc format (and viceversa).

bin2xtc_cg.c
 convert xtc format to plain binary (and viceversa), reducing the number of sites using geometry centers.
 change ngrp in the code

Copy bin2xtc_xy.c to bin2xtc.c
> make all; make install

usage:
> ./bin2xtc source destination direction precision skip_configurations step

source = bin/xtc file (this must exist)
destination = xtc/bin file (this is created)
direction = 1 xtc to bin; -1 bin to xtc
precision = number of digits, 1000 is for 3 digits, i.e. real is 0.xyz
skip_configurations = skip this number of configurations in conversion
step = skip step-1 configurations after one conversion. Starts from first (after skip)
